@carbonenginejs/runtime-sof
===========================

This package ports the CarbonEngine Space Object Factory (SOF) data model and
builder to TypeScript, targeting a serializable Trinity Graph output.

Provenance and ownership
------------------------
CarbonEngine and the EVE Online runtime are the work of Fenris Creations / CCP
Games (CCP ehf.). Class names, field shapes, schema semantics, DNA/SOF data
formats, and build behavior mirrored here are derived from CarbonEngine C++
source used as the authoritative reference (`SpaceObjectFactory/*`), with the
ccpwgl JavaScript library consulted only as optional reference material.

Each ported file carries a `// Source:` header pointing at the CarbonEngine
class it faithfully mirrors.

Non-affiliation
