This package is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by CCP Games /
CCP ehf. or Fenris Creations. "EVE Online" and related marks are the property of
their respective owners. No CarbonEngine or CCP Games source code, proprietary
tools, shaders, or game assets are redistributed in this package; only
independently reimplemented data-shape and behavior derived from studying the
reference material.
